data.description: Welcome to this exquisite two-story home nestled in the desirable Sierra Ridge community of Parker, Colorado. With 1,938 square feet of beautifully finished living space and an additional 868 square feet of unfinished basement potential, this residence offers room to grow. Boasting three bedrooms and three bathrooms, including a luxurious master suite, this home combines comfort with style. The gourmet kitchen features all appliances and is a culinary enthusiast's dream. Enjoy the convenience of central air conditioning, the benefits of a solar system, and the added perk of a two-car garage. With access to a community pool, excellent Douglas County Schools, and proximity to multiple parks and shopping centers, this home delivers the perfect blend of modern living and convenience. Built by Lennar in 2017, it's a rare find in an ideal location.
